57
00:03:36,290 --> 00:03:38,560
<font color="yellow">She doesn't know where her brother is.</font>

58
00:03:38,560 --> 00:03:41,660
<font color="yellow">If they are siblings, she should be Seo Dong Hui. Don't you think so?</font>

59
00:03:42,290 --> 00:03:43,490
