65
00:04:04,260 --> 00:04:07,120
<font color="yellow">Look. It's right. Her name is Oh Dong Hui.</font>

66
00:04:07,790 --> 00:04:11,720
<font color="yellow">You got the wrong person. Come on.</font>

67
00:04:11,820 --> 00:04:13,720
<font color="yellow">No, it can't be. I'm sure it's her.</font>

68
00:04:15,990 --> 00:04:19,220
<font color="yellow">In Taiwan, you were Seo Cheol Min's sister.</font>

69
00:04:20,260 --> 00:04:22,120
<font color="yellow">How is this possible?</font>

70
00:04:22,860 --> 00:04:25,560
