92
00:05:30,160 --> 00:05:33,620
<font color="yellow">You must not try to solve the problem personally.</font>

93
00:05:34,390 --> 00:05:35,890
<font color="yellow">I won't accept it.</font>

94
00:05:35,960 --> 00:05:39,160
<font color="yellow">I'm not trying to solve it personally. I just...</font>

95
00:05:39,160 --> 00:05:41,360
<font color="yellow">It is neither my nor Director Han's problem.</font>

96
00:05:41,790 --> 00:05:43,620
<font color="yellow">It's the legal department's problem.</font>

97
00:05:43,790 --> 00:05:47,260
<font color="yellow">As a matter of fact, it turns out that she's not his real sister.</font>

98
00:05:47,390 --> 00:05:48,660
