104
00:06:22,990 --> 00:06:26,090
<font color="yellow">A second cousin? She can't take responsibility legally?</font>

105
00:06:26,190 --> 00:06:28,190
<font color="yellow">If you live under the same roof, that makes you family.</font>

106
00:06:29,460 --> 00:06:30,620
<font color="yellow">Excuse me.</font>

107
00:06:31,090 --> 00:06:34,760
<font color="yellow">Don't think I'll back down and give up.</font>

108
00:06:34,820 --> 00:06:38,860
<font color="yellow">They might let you go because they are soft, but I assure you I'm not.</font>

109
00:06:39,020 --> 00:06:40,860
<font color="yellow">I'll chase you to the end of the world.</font>

110
00:06:40,960 --> 00:06:43,090
