117
00:07:31,520 --> 00:07:33,820
<font color="yellow">When it's all melted, my class will be over.</font>

118
00:07:34,060 --> 00:07:35,060
<font color="yellow">Okay.</font>

119
00:07:42,460 --> 00:07:43,560
<font color="yellow">Sang Woo.</font>

120
00:07:44,190 --> 00:07:47,520
<font color="yellow">Don't go anywhere. Stay here.</font>

121
00:07:48,090 --> 00:07:50,790
<font color="yellow">- Did you get that? - Yes.</font>

122
00:08:38,890 --> 00:08:39,890
<font color="yellow">Welcome.</font>

123
00:08:42,220 --> 00:08:43,690
<font color="yellow">How can I help you?</font>

124
00:08:53,220 --> 00:08:55,190
