128
00:09:19,130 --> 00:09:20,130
<font color="yellow">Is it him?</font>

129
00:09:21,360 --> 00:09:24,720
<font color="yellow">No, he's my youngest son.</font>

130
00:09:28,660 --> 00:09:29,660
<font color="yellow">I see.</font>

131
00:09:34,890 --> 00:09:37,590
<font color="yellow">Until when did you raise him?</font>

132
00:09:38,390 --> 00:09:40,220
<font color="yellow">I raised him for about a year.</font>

133
00:09:41,560 --> 00:09:46,290
<font color="yellow">I had a flower shop in Bangbae-dong 33 years ago.</font>

134
00:09:46,520 --> 00:09:49,390
<font color="yellow">On a rainy day, a boy was...</font>

135
