<font color="yellow">crying in front of my shop.</font>

136
00:09:52,460 --> 00:09:55,190
<font color="yellow">I asked him why he was crying.</font>

137
00:09:55,460 --> 00:09:58,660
<font color="yellow">He said he was lost and he was sobbing.</font>

138
00:10:00,020 --> 00:10:02,890
<font color="yellow">So I took him to my house and raised him.</font>

139
00:10:03,460 --> 00:10:05,990
<font color="yellow">But someone must have filed a report.</font>

