<font color="yellow">so I visited him every month.</font>

147
00:10:31,760 --> 00:10:33,520
<font color="yellow">When did you last visit him?</font>

148
00:10:34,160 --> 00:10:35,820
<font color="yellow">It's been a long time.</font>

149
00:10:36,160 --> 00:10:38,130
<font color="yellow">He turned 20 when I last saw him.</font>

150
00:10:38,890 --> 00:10:41,390
<font color="yellow">Right. He worked here for a while.</font>

151
00:10:45,990 --> 00:10:48,820
<font color="yellow">Do you have a photo of him?</font>

152
