<font color="yellow">Mr. Lee really hates to let people in his place.</font>

178
00:12:31,320 --> 00:12:33,590
<font color="yellow">I came here just to get the specifications,</font>

179
00:12:33,790 --> 00:12:37,660
<font color="yellow">but if he finds out about you, he might get really angry.</font>

