00:33:04,420 --> 00:33:05,690
<font color="yellow">Yes. Okay.</font>

452
00:33:06,320 --> 00:33:07,520
<font color="yellow">Okay.</font>

453
00:33:20,420 --> 00:33:21,420
<font color="yellow">Hye Joo.</font>

454
00:33:21,760 --> 00:33:22,820
<font color="yellow">What's up, Hee Sook?</font>

455
00:33:22,860 --> 00:33:24,390
<font color="yellow">What did you just say?</font>

