00:33:26,790 --> 00:33:30,260
<font color="yellow">What did you say when I was talking to Mrs. Park?</font>

458
00:33:30,460 --> 00:33:32,790
<font color="yellow">I asked you for a cup of coffee. What's wrong?</font>

459
00:33:33,290 --> 00:33:35,160
<font color="yellow">What did you say before that?</font>

460
00:33:35,190 --> 00:33:37,090
<font color="yellow">What did you call me?</font>

