00:33:37,590 --> 00:33:40,520
<font color="yellow">What did I call you? Well, what did I call you?</font>

462
00:33:40,620 --> 00:33:42,960
<font color="yellow">- I don't remember. - Hye Joo!</font>

463
00:33:43,460 --> 00:33:45,890
<font color="yellow">Why would you yell?</font>

464
00:33:46,520 --> 00:33:50,520
