465
00:33:55,690 --> 00:33:57,090
<font color="yellow">Hey, Ms. Kang,</font>

466
00:33:57,290 --> 00:34:01,020
<font color="yellow">If you do like this one more time, I won't let it slide.</font>

467
00:34:02,090 --> 00:34:03,420
