468
00:34:03,560 --> 00:34:06,960
<font color="yellow">Don't come between Mother and I!</font>

469
00:34:07,230 --> 00:34:09,790
<font color="yellow">I know so many of your secrets...</font>

470
00:34:09,790 --> 00:34:12,060
<font color="yellow">from your three years of working.</font>

471
00:34:12,060 --> 00:34:14,690
<font color="yellow">Do you want me to go on top of this house...</font>

472
00:34:14,690 --> 00:34:18,460
