473
00:34:19,620 --> 00:34:21,120
<font color="yellow">I don't...</font>

474
00:34:21,590 --> 00:34:24,990
<font color="yellow">I don't have any secrets. Okay?</font>

475
00:34:25,360 --> 00:34:28,090
<font color="yellow">Think carefully.</font>

476
00:34:31,960 --> 00:34:34,760
<font color="yellow">For your information, I won't reveal your dating history.</font>

477
00:34:37,990 --> 00:34:41,230
<font color="yellow">Dating history? Do you think I had such a thing?</font>

478
00:34:46,360 --> 00:34:48,390
<font color="yellow">No way.</font>

479
00:34:50,890 --> 00:34:52,190
<font color="yellow">I can't believe this.</font>

480
00:34:52,560 --> 00:34:54,230
<font color="yellow">She's the one who's done wrong things!</font>

481
00:34:59,090 --> 00:35:02,320
<font color="yellow">How do I kick her out?</font>

482
00:35:05,860 --> 00:35:06,960
<font color="yellow">Chang Soo!</font>

483
00:35:08,090 --> 00:35:09,620
<font color="yellow">Are you here to get a medical check-up?</font>

484
00:35:10,090 --> 00:35:12,420
<font color="yellow">- Don't you weigh 100kg? - Stop it!</font>

485
00:35:12,420 --> 00:35:13,460
<font color="yellow">Hey.</font>

486
00:35:14,090 --> 00:35:15,190
<font color="yellow">Let's go.</font>

487
00:35:15,420 --> 00:35:17,890
<font color="yellow">We don't have time. I have to get done fast and go.</font>

488
00:35:18,060 --> 00:35:19,090
<font color="yellow">Okay.</font>

489
00:35:32,990 --> 00:35:34,730
<font color="yellow">You weigh 47kg.</font>

490
00:35:36,890 --> 00:35:39,860
<font color="yellow">Goodness! What are you doing?</font>

491
00:35:39,860 --> 00:35:43,060
<font color="yellow">My mother said she'll give me extra pocket money if I weigh 99kg.</font>

492
00:35:43,620 --> 00:35:45,820
<font color="yellow">Put on your clothes. I will deduct 1kg from your weight.</font>

493
00:35:46,290 --> 00:35:47,890
<font color="yellow">You're big enough.</font>

494
00:35:50,890 --> 00:35:53,120
<font color="yellow">You weigh 121kg.</font>

495
00:35:53,120 --> 00:35:55,860
<font color="yellow">When I subtract 1kg, it becomes 120kg.</font>

496
00:35:56,990 --> 00:35:59,020
<font color="yellow">Say good bye to your allowance.</font>

497
00:35:59,020 --> 00:36:00,660
<font color="yellow">No!</font>

498
00:36:00,760 --> 00:36:01,790
<font color="yellow">No!</font>

499
00:36:05,890 --> 00:36:08,820
<font color="yellow">Stop making a fuss. You look like you could even cook a cow.</font>

500
00:36:08,820 --> 00:36:10,620
<font color="yellow">But it really hurts.</font>

501
00:36:11,620 --> 00:36:13,420
<font color="yellow">What do you think your blood type is?</font>

502
00:36:14,090 --> 00:36:16,660
<font color="yellow">- B. - How about you?</font>

503
00:36:16,760 --> 00:36:17,790
<font color="yellow">Me?</font>

504
00:36:18,730 --> 00:36:19,790
<font color="yellow">I don't know.</font>

505
00:36:19,990 --> 00:36:21,290
<font color="yellow">Is it C?</font>

506
00:36:21,420 --> 00:36:24,560
<font color="yellow">There's only "hepatitis C".</font>

507
00:36:24,890 --> 00:36:27,190
<font color="yellow">I remembered it. It's O.</font>

508
00:36:27,490 --> 00:36:29,160
<font color="yellow">- You're not joking, right? - No.</font>

509
00:36:31,120 --> 00:36:32,260
<font color="yellow">Am I wrong?</font>

510
00:36:32,660 --> 00:36:34,420
<font color="yellow">I think it's right. Is it right?</font>

511
00:36:36,160 --> 00:36:37,160
<font color="yellow">Ji Hoon</font>

512
00:36:38,230 --> 00:36:39,460
<font color="yellow">Are you not going to eat your corn dog?</font>

513
00:36:39,490 --> 00:36:40,960
<font color="yellow">We must eat because we had a blood test.</font>

514
00:36:41,990 --> 00:36:44,260
<font color="yellow">By the way, don't you have tutoring?</font>

515
00:36:44,760 --> 00:36:47,730
<font color="yellow">Attend the tutoring. Otherwise, your mom will be very upset.</font>

516
00:37:01,160 --> 00:37:04,560
<font color="yellow">You're not going to eat it, right? Then I'll have yours.</font>

517
00:37:06,990 --> 00:37:07,990
<font color="yellow">Chang Soo.</font>

518
00:37:09,730 --> 00:37:10,730
<font color="yellow">I...</font>

519
00:37:11,860 --> 00:37:13,260
<font color="yellow">don't want to live.</font>

520
00:37:14,120 --> 00:37:15,190
<font color="yellow">What?</font>

521
00:37:18,520 --> 00:37:19,730
<font color="yellow">Because of my mom,</font>

522
00:37:21,820 --> 00:37:23,390
<font color="yellow">I might die.</font>

523
00:37:24,290 --> 00:37:25,390
<font color="yellow">Hey!</font>

524
00:37:53,360 --> 00:37:55,190
<font color="yellow">Let go of me. Let's talk later.</font>

525
00:37:55,190 --> 00:37:57,490
<font color="yellow">Let's talk today. I will tell you everything.</font>

526
00:38:10,360 --> 00:38:11,620
<font color="yellow">Can you drink soju?</font>

527
00:38:12,190 --> 00:38:14,660
<font color="yellow">What does that mean? That was a sharp question.</font>

528
00:38:15,520 --> 00:38:17,790
<font color="yellow">I was just asking if you could drink soju.</font>

529
00:38:19,120 --> 00:38:22,490
<font color="yellow">I think I've never drunk soju with you.</font>

530
00:38:22,730 --> 00:38:25,520
<font color="yellow">Of course. I love wine.</font>

531
00:38:26,420 --> 00:38:27,520
<font color="yellow">Of course.</font>

532
00:38:37,160 --> 00:38:38,160
<font color="yellow">Actually,</font>

533
00:38:39,160 --> 00:38:41,590
<font color="yellow">I knew she was Seo Cheol Min's little sister from the start.</font>

534
00:38:43,660 --> 00:38:46,190
<font color="yellow">I don't know if it's okay for me to say this or not,</font>

535
00:38:46,760 --> 00:38:47,820
<font color="yellow">but I just let her go.</font>

536
00:38:49,360 --> 00:38:50,490
<font color="yellow">Why?</font>

537
00:38:51,320 --> 00:38:54,490
<font color="yellow">I told you before. It seems like she can't afford it.</font>

538
00:38:54,490 --> 00:38:58,490
<font color="yellow">But if you let her go, you'd have to let everyone else go, too.</font>

539
00:38:58,490 --> 00:38:59,660
<font color="yellow">I know.</font>

540
00:39:00,230 --> 00:39:02,020
<font color="yellow">But when you live life,</font>

541
00:39:03,020 --> 00:39:05,120
<font color="yellow">there are people who really doesn't have anything.</font>

542
00:39:05,360 --> 00:39:07,420
<font color="yellow">But they should at least take the legal responsibility</font>

543
00:39:07,520 --> 00:39:10,020
<font color="yellow">for what they have done.</font>

544
00:39:10,460 --> 00:39:13,120
<font color="yellow">Isn't that better for their lives as well?</font>

545
00:39:13,320 --> 00:39:16,890
<font color="yellow">You can't just do something bad and refuse to be arrested.</font>

546
00:39:18,890 --> 00:39:20,090
<font color="yellow">Stop drinking.</font>

547
00:39:20,420 --> 00:39:22,190
<font color="yellow">You never drink this fast.</font>

548
00:39:22,690 --> 00:39:23,730
<font color="yellow">What's wrong with you?</font>

549
00:39:29,730 --> 00:39:30,730
<font color="yellow">You know,</font>

550
00:39:31,590 --> 00:39:33,730
<font color="yellow">I have a rule for cutting people some slack.</font>

551
00:39:34,690 --> 00:39:38,320
<font color="yellow">When you work, you meet all kinds of con-artist-like people.</font>

552
00:39:38,790 --> 00:39:42,320
<font color="yellow">I first try not to let them get to me. Then if I get tricked...</font>

553
00:39:42,320 --> 00:39:43,520
<font color="yellow">like how I get tricked by Cheol Min, I won't cut him slack.</font>

554
00:39:44,020 --> 00:39:46,520
<font color="yellow">I'd follow him to the end...</font>

555
00:39:46,520 --> 00:39:47,990
<font color="yellow">and make him pay for it. If he can't pay,</font>

556
00:39:48,660 --> 00:39:50,020
<font color="yellow">I might send him to jail.</font>

557
00:39:50,120 --> 00:39:52,460
<font color="yellow">Then why did you do that to Seo Cheol Min's sister?</font>

558
00:39:56,490 --> 00:39:59,290
<font color="yellow">- I think she knows her place. - What do you mean?</font>

559
00:39:59,620 --> 00:40:01,090
<font color="yellow">It looks like she knows...</font>

560
00:40:01,560 --> 00:40:03,460
<font color="yellow">that what her brother did was embarrassing.</font>

561
00:40:04,560 --> 00:40:07,090
<font color="yellow">She honestly accepted that her brother has made mistakes.</font>

562
00:40:07,690 --> 00:40:09,790
<font color="yellow">I thought it was amazing to see her trying to pay for it.</font>

563
00:40:10,230 --> 00:40:11,260
<font color="yellow">Did you think that was amazing?</font>

564
00:40:13,020 --> 00:40:14,060
<font color="yellow">Yes.</font>

565
00:40:14,620 --> 00:40:15,620
<font color="yellow">I did.</font>

566
00:40:16,490 --> 00:40:18,190
<font color="yellow">But how much will she be able to pay back?</font>

567
00:40:18,260 --> 00:40:20,520
<font color="yellow">I don't think there's any way for her to pay back everything.</font>

568
00:40:21,730 --> 00:40:24,320
<font color="yellow">Isn't it enough for her to know that it was wrong?</font>

569
00:40:25,120 --> 00:40:26,460
<font color="yellow">That's why I let her go.</font>

570
00:40:26,490 --> 00:40:28,460
<font color="yellow">Even if Producer Kim was throwing a fit?</font>

571
00:40:30,260 --> 00:40:33,290
<font color="yellow">- I feel bad for Producer Kim. - How about me?</font>

572
00:40:35,520 --> 00:40:37,190
<font color="yellow">Don't you feel bad for me?</font>

573
00:40:39,460 --> 00:40:40,520
<font color="yellow">For you...</font>

574
00:40:42,160 --> 00:40:43,620
<font color="yellow">I feel sorry about everything.</font>

575
00:40:48,960 --> 00:40:50,090
<font color="yellow">You're a bad guy.</font>

576
00:40:57,120 --> 00:40:58,560
<font color="yellow">Then, marry me.</font>

577
00:41:12,420 --> 00:41:13,590
<font color="yellow">I can't do that.</font>

578
00:41:14,460 --> 00:41:15,460
<font color="yellow">Why?</font>

579
00:41:17,520 --> 00:41:19,190
<font color="yellow">Because I know where I stand.</font>

580
00:41:20,360 --> 00:41:21,660
<font color="yellow">What do you mean?</font>

581
00:41:25,190 --> 00:41:26,890
<font color="yellow">Let me ask you a question, too.</font>

582
00:41:28,660 --> 00:41:30,190
<font color="yellow">Can you eat fishcake?</font>

583
00:41:32,460 --> 00:41:33,520
<font color="yellow">How about sundae?</font>

584
00:41:37,020 --> 00:41:38,060
<font color="yellow">Forget it.</font>

585
00:41:39,230 --> 00:41:41,490
<font color="yellow">- Seong Joon. - Excuse me.</font>

586
00:41:41,790 --> 00:41:43,420
<font color="yellow">Can you give me some fishcake?</font>

587
00:41:43,890 --> 00:41:46,090
<font color="yellow">- And bring some sundae, too. - Okay.</font>

588
00:42:35,620 --> 00:42:36,660
<font color="yellow">You're home.</font>

589
00:42:49,490 --> 00:42:51,960
<font color="yellow">How did Producer Kim catch you?</font>

590
00:42:53,620 --> 00:42:55,620
<font color="yellow">You saw the picket I had, right?</font>

591
00:42:55,660 --> 00:42:58,090
<font color="yellow">How can I not be spotted with something like that?</font>

592
00:43:00,020 --> 00:43:01,090
<font color="yellow">Anyway.</font>

593
00:43:01,660 --> 00:43:05,060
<font color="yellow">I'm sorry, I must have put you in a bad spot today.</font>

594
00:43:05,360 --> 00:43:08,660
<font color="yellow">Is that why you're sad? Because you feel embarrassed?</font>

595
00:43:09,360 --> 00:43:12,290
<font color="yellow">No, I was thinking what I did to deserve such brother.</font>

596
00:43:13,390 --> 00:43:17,460
<font color="yellow">It takes a lot to hurt my ego since I went through a lot.</font>

597
00:43:18,190 --> 00:43:19,190
<font color="yellow">But...</font>

598
00:43:21,290 --> 00:43:23,620
<font color="yellow">I've been thinking for the whole day,</font>

599
00:43:24,060 --> 00:43:27,090
<font color="yellow">but I have no idea how to pay the money back.</font>

600
00:43:28,890 --> 00:43:30,090
<font color="yellow">Exactly.</font>

601
00:43:30,760 --> 00:43:34,160
<font color="yellow">I think I felt better when I was trying to get money out of you.</font>

602
00:43:34,760 --> 00:43:36,320
<font color="yellow">Look who's talking.</font>

603
00:43:37,230 --> 00:43:41,290
<font color="yellow">You asked me what I was going to do for you in return.</font>

604
00:43:41,560 --> 00:43:42,990
<font color="yellow">I was only joking.</font>

605
00:43:42,990 --> 00:43:45,960
<font color="yellow">Put yourself in my shoes. Would you have seen it as a joke?</font>

606
00:43:53,220 --> 00:43:57,160
<font color="yellow">It's Producer Kim. He called me 20 times today.</font>

607
00:43:59,790 --> 00:44:02,660
<font color="yellow">Yes, Producer Kim. I'm home.</font>

608
00:44:02,890 --> 00:44:04,360
<font color="yellow">I just got here.</font>

609
00:44:06,320 --> 00:44:09,360
<font color="yellow">What are you saying? How can I put my grandmother on the phone?</font>

610
00:44:09,620 --> 00:44:11,860
<font color="yellow">I'll visit you tomorrow.</font>

611
00:44:11,990 --> 00:44:13,260
<font color="yellow">Please. I beg you.</font>

612
00:44:16,320 --> 00:44:17,520
<font color="yellow">Okay.</font>

613
00:44:18,020 --> 00:44:20,060
<font color="yellow">I'll see you tomorrow.</font>

614
00:44:22,320 --> 00:44:25,190
<font color="yellow">Is he blackmailing you?</font>

615
00:44:25,460 --> 00:44:28,720
<font color="yellow">Yes. I think a loan shark might be more suitable...</font>

616
00:44:29,060 --> 00:44:30,890
<font color="yellow">for him than a producer.</font>

617
00:44:35,990 --> 00:44:37,190
<font color="yellow">We can't fix what's already been done.</font>

618
00:44:37,960 --> 00:44:39,360
<font color="yellow">Let's go to Taiwan again.</font>

619
00:44:40,460 --> 00:44:41,460
<font color="yellow">What?</font>

620
00:44:42,160 --> 00:44:43,990
<font color="yellow">Let's go to Taiwan to catch your brother.</font>

621
00:44:45,620 --> 00:44:48,090
<font color="yellow">- That doesn't make any sense. - Why doesn't it?</font>

622
00:44:48,520 --> 00:44:51,560
<font color="yellow">What kind of a brother tortures his family like this?</font>

623
00:44:52,160 --> 00:44:55,260
<font color="yellow">If we catch him, everything will be solved.</font>

624
00:44:55,820 --> 00:44:59,120
<font color="yellow">He must take responsibility of his actions, not you.</font>

625
00:44:59,190 --> 00:45:01,890
<font color="yellow">- Do you think I want to? - Then what?</font>

626
00:45:02,890 --> 00:45:05,490
<font color="yellow">I wish that either he gets caught...</font>

627
00:45:05,790 --> 00:45:07,860
<font color="yellow">or returns quickly.</font>

628
00:45:08,820 --> 00:45:10,360
<font color="yellow">But until then,</font>

629
00:45:11,060 --> 00:45:13,860
<font color="yellow">I need to protect my grandmother.</font>

630
00:45:15,020 --> 00:45:16,690
<font color="yellow">As this is what happened,</font>

631
00:45:16,890 --> 00:45:19,960
<font color="yellow">she must have caught on a bit about Cheol Min's situation.</font>

632
00:45:20,890 --> 00:45:22,020
<font color="yellow">Still,</font>

